<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 lán lán de dà hǎi lán lán de tiān biān
 yuán yě shàng wān wān de xiǎo lù cūn luò shàng kōng niǎo niǎo chuī yān
 bù lùn wǒ men xiāng lí duō yáo yuǎn huān jù hái shì fēn sàn
 zǒng yǒu yī tiáo lù bǎ wǒ men xiāng lián
 cóng lái méi yǒu wàng jì wǒ men duì shén de chéng nuò
 shǒu lā shǒu wǒ men xiǎng shuō de tài duō tài duō
 gòng tóng yǒu yī jù huà dài tì qiān yán wàn yǔ
 yào jiāng fú yīn chuán biàn shì wǒ men gòng tóng de xīn yuàn.</lyrics>
<title>zǒng yǒu yī tiáo lù bǎ wǒ men xiāng lián 迦南215</title>
